  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8566829">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8566829/" class="title-link">一个不断死人的时代</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8566829"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/MovieL/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1128221-95.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/MovieL/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">木卫二</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-05-28"
      class="main-meta">2017-05-28 01:00:06</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8566829_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  川本三郎是日本著名文艺评论家，评论村上春树很有名气，在《电影旬报》上有开专栏。 虽也借他人之口自嘲，“什么头衔都没有的家伙，似乎就会被冠上『评论家』的样子。” 这本《我爱过的那个时代》，就是妻夫木聪和松山研一主演的《昔日的我》原著，回忆了他人生中明亮又黑暗，...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8566829_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8566829_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





